Description:
    Creates a default AngularJS app in LiveScript

Example:
    yo angular-ls [--minsafe]

    This will create:
        Gruntfile.coffee
        bower.json

        app/index.html
        app/scripts/your-app-name-here.ls
        app/scripts/controllers/main.ls
        app/bower_components/angular/angular.ls
        app/styles/main.css
        app/views/main.html

        test/spec/controllers/main.ls
